body: {"agents": [{"id": "price_refresh", "name": "Price Refresh", "description": "Refresh stock prices from Finnhub", "schedules": {"market_open": "cron(45 14 ? * MON-FRI *)", "intraday": "rate(30 minutes)", "market_close": "cron(30 20 ? * MON-FRI *)"}, "lastRun": null}, {"id": "technicals_refresh", "name": "Technicals Refresh", "description": "Compute technical indicators from candle data", "schedules": {"daily": "cron(30 21 ? * MON-FRI *)"}, "lastRun": null}, {"id": "signal_generation", "name": "Signal Generation", "description": "Generate AI BUY/HOLD/SELL signals from all data", "schedules": {"daily": "cron(0 22 ? * MON-FRI *)", "weekly_full": "cron(0 8 ? * SAT *)"}, "lastRun": null}, {"id": "fundamentals_refresh", "name": "Fundamentals Refresh", "description": "Refresh fundamental data from SEC EDGAR", "schedules": {"weekly": "cron(0 10 ? * SUN *)"}, "lastRun": null}, {"id": "feed_compile", "name": "Feed Compile", "description": "Compile the daily signal feed from latest data", "schedules": {"daily": "cron(30 10 ? * MON-FRI *)"}, "lastRun": null}]}
